# Taxpayer data — NEVER commit
# User convention: data lives at ~/TaxData/, never inside this repo.
# These patterns are defense-in-depth in case someone copies data into the tree by mistake.
*.tax
*.T[0-9][0-9]
TaxData/
tax-data/
user-data/
**/return.json
!skill/schemas/return.schema.json
!skill/fixtures/**/return.json
!skill/tests/**/return.json

